	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's hard to say, but I highly doubt the MMC1 is the cause of your scrabled graphics. The terrible connector should be at 99,99% what causes you problems. Anyway if the PCB of retro zone make better contact then maybe that will fix the problem. You'd have to be able to disolder both roms without damaging the pins which is very hard to do (I only suceeded once).

		

		</td>
